description.narrative:
In this project, we aim to do the following: 
1. To contribute to the body of knowledge on how best to reach and engage young sex workers and to design culturally and age-appropriate services; 
6. To further disseminate and implement normative guidance and best practices to reach and serve young sex workers; 
7. To promote network building among young sex workers and other key populations and allow them to learn about their rights and to advocate to fulfill these rights; 
8. To increase demand for and uptake of services among young sex workers by upscaling tailor made youth services and ensuring that ‘traditional’ services become young key population friendly.
